<p>3.<a href="http://www.ityouknow.com/life/2019/08/13/shenzhen-10year.html">深圳流水线工厂，我差点和主管打了起来 ~ 2009</a></p>

<p>4.<a href="http://www.ityouknow.com/life/2019/09/12/fushikang-10year.html">富士康14跳被我赶上了，流水线车间真的没有梦想 ~ 2009</a></p>

<p>5.<a href="http://www.ityouknow.com/life/2019/10/31/training-10year.html">我在培训机构折腾的经历，再和大家聊聊这个行业 ~ 2010</a></p>

